28:27.740 --> 28:30.109
Oh, and there's her friend,
Dr. Lambert.

28:30.142 --> 28:32.711
Well, let me tell y'all
about these two.

28:32.745 --> 28:36.615
Lana had her friend,
Dr. Lambert,

28:36.648 --> 28:40.853
prescribe my son
psychosis-inducing drugs.

28:40.887 --> 28:42.588
(crowd gasping, murmuring)

28:44.623 --> 28:49.695
My son suffers from
mental illness already.

28:49.728 --> 28:51.630
Who would do that?

28:54.566 --> 28:57.436
Diana Dubois,
the pillar of your community.

28:57.469 --> 28:58.437
(chuckles)

29:00.306 --> 29:01.941
She's a kidnapper.

29:01.974 --> 29:05.444
She kidnapped my grandbaby,
my son's daughter Bella.

29:05.477 --> 29:10.716
She also paid her own nephew
to infiltrate my family

29:10.749 --> 29:13.285
and rip son's heart
out of his chest.

29:13.319 --> 29:14.787
(crowd murmuring)

29:14.821 --> 29:16.188
What?

29:18.657 --> 29:20.927
These are my babies, okay?

29:20.960 --> 29:23.562
They're good boys.
They're talented.

29:23.595 --> 29:26.465
They might be messy sometimes,

29:26.498 --> 29:28.634
but they didn't deserve
to be treated like that

29:28.667 --> 29:31.337
-by this bitch.
-(crowd gasping)

29:31.370 --> 29:33.772
Good-bye, babies.
Y'all did a good job today.

29:33.806 --> 29:34.706
Thank you.

29:45.017 --> 29:46.853
Nanny, bring her bag, please.

29:46.886 --> 29:49.421
Hurry. Hurry.

29:49.455 --> 29:51.824
(door opens, closes)

29:51.858 --> 29:53.826
HAKEEM:
I'll take my daughter.

29:53.860 --> 29:55.794
The hell you will.

29:57.997 --> 30:00.066
I'm gonna need you to sign this.

30:03.702 --> 30:05.938
What is this?

30:05.972 --> 30:07.940
We got videotapes
of you and Diana,

30:07.974 --> 30:10.176
when Bella was supposed
to be missing.

30:10.209 --> 30:12.344
Warren told us where they were.

30:14.380 --> 30:17.683
You're an accessory
to a kidnapping.

30:21.020 --> 30:23.990
Hakeem, I...

30:24.023 --> 30:25.791
I can't go back to jail.

30:25.824 --> 30:27.927
Then sign it.

30:29.528 --> 30:32.531
-Give her to me.
-No, please. Please.

30:32.564 --> 30:35.301
(sobbing): Please, don't take
my baby again, please.

30:35.334 --> 30:37.169
Don't take her from me.

30:37.203 --> 30:39.205
Like you took her away from me?

30:39.238 --> 30:40.206
Huh?

30:40.239 --> 30:41.740
Please, don't.

30:41.773 --> 30:44.676
Stop crying, Anika.
It upsets Bella.

30:44.710 --> 30:48.847
Look, I know what it's like
to grow up without a mother.

30:48.881 --> 30:51.383
I would never do that
to my daughter.

30:51.417 --> 30:53.385
You're gonna be
a part of her life,

30:53.419 --> 30:54.987
but the BS stops right here.

30:55.021 --> 30:57.489
You will no longer
use her as a pawn

30:57.523 --> 31:01.093
to get to me or my family.

31:01.127 --> 31:03.062
Do you understand me?

31:03.095 --> 31:05.264
Yes.

31:05.297 --> 31:08.267
I understand.

31:08.300 --> 31:09.936
But the tapes...

31:09.969 --> 31:12.571
Nobody got to see them.

31:12.604 --> 31:14.706
But don't ever forget
we got them.

31:14.740 --> 31:17.409
And there's no statute
of limitation on kidnapping.

31:21.280 --> 31:23.615
Sign it.

31:28.487 --> 31:30.722
Oh, if I were you,

31:30.756 --> 31:33.926
I wouldn't go to
the Captain's Ball downstairs.

31:33.960 --> 31:35.561
It's a Red Wedding down there.

31:45.804 --> 31:47.706
Let's go, Bella.

31:47.739 --> 31:49.275
It's time to go home.

31:53.279 --> 31:55.181
(sobbing)

32:06.592 --> 32:08.460
So there you have it,
ladies and gentlemen.

32:08.494 --> 32:11.430
-Let's go. Take me home.
-Didn't you hear them?

32:11.463 --> 32:13.132
They have a signed confession.

32:13.165 --> 32:14.266
Trying to save yourself?

32:14.300 --> 32:16.835
They have a coerced confession.

32:16.868 --> 32:18.904
You kidnapped a baby?

32:18.937 --> 32:20.006
Yeah, she did.

32:23.142 --> 32:26.645
Cookie, I am very sorry.

32:26.678 --> 32:29.348
And I hope to God
Andre makes a full recovery.

32:29.381 --> 32:30.849
Thank you.

32:30.882 --> 32:33.152
And I'm sorry I ever got
involved in any of this.

32:33.185 --> 32:35.187
Shut up.

32:35.221 --> 32:37.756
COOKIE:
Diana Dubois. (chuckles)

32:37.789 --> 32:41.593
She ain't nothing
but a common criminal.

32:41.627 --> 32:43.462
(crowd murmuring)

32:44.796 --> 32:47.199
You...

32:47.233 --> 32:48.834
your gimp-legged husband

32:48.867 --> 32:52.171
and your intellectually
challenged children

32:52.204 --> 32:57.209
are not now nor will you ever be
fit to judge me.

32:57.243 --> 32:59.545
And as for the rest of you,
shaking your heads,

32:59.578 --> 33:02.481
batting your eyelashes,
trembling in your shoes

33:02.514 --> 33:04.616
and backing away...

33:04.650 --> 33:06.618
Pathetic.

33:06.652 --> 33:09.055
If it weren't for me,
half of you wouldn't be here.

33:09.088 --> 33:11.790
COOKIE:
I feel sorry for you, Diana.

33:11.823 --> 33:14.793
My family would never turn on me

33:14.826 --> 33:17.196
the way yours have
on you tonight.

33:17.229 --> 33:19.065
-Really?
-Really.

33:19.098 --> 33:20.832
-Excuse me.
-DIANA: Is that why you spent

33:20.866 --> 33:22.534
the better part
of your life in prison?

33:22.568 --> 33:24.303
Oh, I wouldn't call it
the better part, honey.

33:24.336 --> 33:25.571
I'm just getting started.

33:25.604 --> 33:28.907
-Ms. Dubois.
-Yes, she's right over there.

33:28.940 --> 33:30.909
We have a warrant for
your arrest in the kidnapping

33:30.942 --> 33:32.878
-of Bella Lyon.
-(crowd murmuring)

33:36.715 --> 33:39.085
Do not... touch me.

33:41.453 --> 33:42.888
COOKIE:
I wouldn't resist arrest, honey.

33:42.921 --> 33:44.890
-They might put you
in a choke hold. -(laughter)

33:44.923 --> 33:46.425
WOMAN:
Yes, Cookie!

33:46.458 --> 33:48.026
MAN:
Go, Cookie!

33:48.060 --> 33:50.329
WOMAN 2:
Long live Queen Cookie!

33:50.362 --> 33:52.831
-Enjoy your prison life!
-WOMAN 3: You tell 'em, girl!

33:52.864 --> 33:56.168
COOKIE: Why don't we spark up
this band, honey?

33:56.202 --> 33:58.770
Let's get this party started.

34:02.040 --> 34:03.475
-(pounding on door)
-One second, Jamal.

34:04.976 --> 34:07.446
(pounding on door)

34:07.479 --> 34:09.515
Get back.

34:09.548 --> 34:11.049
-Angelo.
-Shh.

34:11.083 --> 34:14.086
-Angelo...
-See? See?

34:14.120 --> 34:15.721
-Wait a minute. Listen.
-I told you to shut your...

34:15.754 --> 34:18.023
-Warren, your plane leaves
in less than two... -Ah.

34:18.056 --> 34:21.460
Oh, guys. Come on.

34:21.493 --> 34:23.895
Isn't this sweet?

34:23.929 --> 34:26.798
(laughs)

34:26.832 --> 34:30.869
-Angelo, this...
-Get your ass back.

34:30.902 --> 34:33.439
This is the part,
this is the part of the story

34:33.472 --> 34:36.208
where Romeo falls
into Juliet's arms, right?

34:36.242 --> 34:37.476
-Come on, man.
-And they get to have

34:37.509 --> 34:38.544
really hot makeup sex.

34:38.577 --> 34:40.912
-Angelo, all this...
-Listen. Nah, nope!

34:40.946 --> 34:42.781
Nope.

34:44.450 --> 34:45.817
Are we at that part
of the story?

34:48.320 --> 34:49.955
-Angelo, listen...
-This is how it ends.

34:49.988 --> 34:51.890
Angelo!

34:51.923 --> 34:54.059
No! Jamal!

34:54.092 --> 34:55.627
-Give it to me!
-Stop it!

34:55.661 --> 34:57.629
(both grunting)

35:06.672 --> 35:07.973
(grunts):
Jamal!

35:08.006 --> 35:10.642
Let go! Stop it!

35:10.676 --> 35:12.043
(gunshot)

35:14.146 --> 35:15.647
Wait a minute.

35:15.681 --> 35:17.683
Uh, wait a minute.

35:17.716 --> 35:19.451
Jamal.

35:22.688 --> 35:24.956
-Oh, no.
-Angelo.

35:24.990 --> 35:26.892
-Angelo.
-Oh, no.

35:28.059 --> 35:29.995
(Angelo groaning)

35:34.633 --> 35:37.836
I'm all right. It's my shoulder.
I'm good.

35:40.572 --> 35:42.841
Angelo. Hey, you all right?

35:42.874 --> 35:44.443
Come on, man. Please.

35:44.476 --> 35:47.213
Come on, come on, man.
Come on, come on.

35:52.551 --> 35:54.486
(line ringing)

35:56.988 --> 35:58.957
WOMAN:
911. What's your emergency?

35:58.990 --> 36:01.627
Yeah, um, I need a...
I need someone

36:01.660 --> 36:03.995
at, um, the Sixth Street Motel
in Long Island.

36:04.029 --> 36:05.497
There's been a shooting.

36:05.531 --> 36:08.166
Yeah.

36:08.200 --> 36:10.101
I think someone is dead.

36:18.244 --> 36:19.678
LUCIOUS:
So, you headed home?

36:19.711 --> 36:21.012
COOKIE:
Yeah. Aren't you? I'm tired.

36:21.046 --> 36:23.249
I want to stop by the hospital
and let Andre know

36:23.282 --> 36:25.150
we took care of things for him.

36:25.183 --> 36:27.152
-Can you tell him I love him?
-Of course.

36:27.185 --> 36:28.654
Let him know
I'll be there tomorrow.

36:28.687 --> 36:31.590
I am tired tonight.

36:31.623 --> 36:34.192
-So, Cook?
-Yeah?

36:34.226 --> 36:36.828
Are we good?

36:36.862 --> 36:38.664
Um, yeah.

36:38.697 --> 36:40.098
W-Why you say that?

36:40.131 --> 36:42.268
This is me, baby. I'm back.

36:42.301 --> 36:43.669
(chuckles)

36:43.702 --> 36:45.070
You're back just like that?

36:45.103 --> 36:46.672
Well, not just like that.

36:46.705 --> 36:51.109
I'm still seeing the music
and hearing the colors, and...

36:51.142 --> 36:52.911
I'm kind of Lucious-plus now.

36:54.780 --> 36:57.949
I'm just hoping you and me
can get back to where we were.

37:00.652 --> 37:02.821
Back to where we were?
What do you mean?

37:06.992 --> 37:10.396
Either you're moving
into my bedroom, babe,

37:10.429 --> 37:12.331
or you're moving
out of the house.

37:14.400 --> 37:16.302
(chuckles)

37:18.404 --> 37:20.306
Well, I guess
I'll be moving out.

37:22.140 --> 37:24.976
'Cause if you're really back,
Lucious...

37:27.012 --> 37:30.816
...I really think we should
take our time this go-round.

37:34.853 --> 37:36.822
You know how much
I love you, right?

37:36.855 --> 37:38.524
I love you, too. (chuckles)

37:43.995 --> 37:45.497
Webb, get my baby home.

37:45.531 --> 37:48.734
Good work in there tonight,
Fred Astaire.

37:48.767 --> 37:50.669
(chuckles)

37:55.841 --> 37:57.643
Been a really great help to me

37:57.676 --> 37:59.678
for these last few months,
Sheri.

37:59.711 --> 38:01.780
I've really enjoyed
getting to know you.

38:01.813 --> 38:02.981
Yeah. Me, too.

38:03.014 --> 38:04.249
I'm gonna send you a ticket,

38:04.282 --> 38:05.584
so you can come visit me
in Barbados.

38:05.617 --> 38:07.085
-All right? -Okay.
-GISELLE: Eddie!

38:07.118 --> 38:08.320
That'd be nice.

38:08.354 --> 38:10.255
-Great.
-Eddie!

38:10.288 --> 38:11.823
Look...

38:11.857 --> 38:13.091
Who is that?

38:13.124 --> 38:14.960
-It's my ex-wife.
-Who is this?

38:14.993 --> 38:16.628
How old are you? 15?

38:16.662 --> 38:18.530
You know what?
She happens to be 32.

38:18.564 --> 38:21.166
-Whatever. -And she's an
accomplished assistant engineer.

38:21.199 --> 38:22.968
What do you want, Giselle?

38:23.001 --> 38:24.370
Want me to wash
your Maserati for you?

38:24.403 --> 38:26.271
Look, I want you to tell me

38:26.304 --> 38:28.540
that this business with Steve
Lawrence is just a bad dream.

38:28.574 --> 38:30.175
What are you talking about?

38:30.208 --> 38:32.043
Oh, my God.

38:32.077 --> 38:34.480
You don't even know.

38:36.582 --> 38:38.517
Here. You didn't see this?

38:40.185 --> 38:44.356
"Steve Lawrence's
Multibillion-Dollar Scam."

38:44.390 --> 38:46.992
"Lawrence Another
Bernie Madoff."

38:47.025 --> 38:48.994
"Wealthy Clients Bankrupted."

38:49.027 --> 38:50.496
Is this real?

38:50.529 --> 38:52.230
You're damn straight
it's real, Eddie.

38:52.263 --> 38:53.899
We're broke.

38:53.932 --> 38:55.534
Wiped out.

38:55.567 --> 38:57.202
You, me, the other ex-wife--

38:57.235 --> 38:59.304
that's if you had her in the
same investments you had me in--

38:59.337 --> 39:00.839
the kids from both marriages.

39:00.872 --> 39:02.641
I saw the returns.
I-I saw them myself.

39:02.674 --> 39:04.376
It was a Ponzi scheme.

39:04.410 --> 39:06.678
He was robbing Peter
to pay Paul.

39:09.347 --> 39:12.384
Okay, what are we gonna do? Huh?

39:15.687 --> 39:18.724
It's not a problem, Giselle.

39:18.757 --> 39:20.559
You see where we are, right?

39:20.592 --> 39:22.428
Empire. So?

39:22.461 --> 39:24.430
I've been ensconced here
for the last few months.

39:24.463 --> 39:26.732
I've been helping them
stay afloat.

39:26.765 --> 39:28.734
Cookie and Lucious would love

39:28.767 --> 39:31.002
for me to stick around Empire,
help them out.

39:31.036 --> 39:32.938
Hey.

39:32.971 --> 39:34.372
What?

39:34.406 --> 39:36.274
I got some ideas.

39:36.307 --> 39:37.943
I heard you.

39:37.976 --> 39:39.277
Let me handle this.

39:53.992 --> 39:56.462
(Cookie sighs)

40:00.098 --> 40:03.469
Yeah, just take all of
that stuff to my place.

40:03.502 --> 40:06.472
MAN: All right, let's move those
right out to the truck.

40:06.505 --> 40:08.440
(sighs)

40:14.179 --> 40:16.515
Think I'm gonna
stay here tonight.

40:28.093 --> 40:30.161
Andre?

40:30.195 --> 40:32.263
Can you hear me, cheap seats?

40:32.297 --> 40:34.199
(chuckles softly)

40:36.034 --> 40:38.637
Took some doing to find out
where they had you hidden away.

40:40.472 --> 40:42.974
You been keeping
your mouth shut?

40:43.008 --> 40:44.976
I didn't think so, either.

40:45.010 --> 40:46.678
Shine.

40:46.712 --> 40:48.647
-Hey.
-What are you doing here?

40:48.680 --> 40:51.750
Hey, just checking on Andre.

40:51.783 --> 40:53.485
How you doing, Lucious?

40:53.519 --> 40:54.986
How'd you find him?

40:55.020 --> 40:57.789
(scoffs) You ain't
the only one with juice.

40:57.823 --> 40:59.758
Why you hiding him, anyway?

40:59.791 --> 41:01.359
I'm not hiding him.

41:01.392 --> 41:03.361
I'm protecting him.

41:03.394 --> 41:05.631
I didn't know
y'all became friends.

41:06.898 --> 41:09.367
Andre is my boy.

41:09.400 --> 41:12.638
We squashed all that petty stuff
a long time ago.

41:12.671 --> 41:15.140
Anyway, I'm gonna let you
have some time with your son.

41:15.173 --> 41:16.341
-Thank you, brother.
-All right.

41:23.081 --> 41:24.516
Hey.

41:24.550 --> 41:26.985
Can you hear me?

41:27.018 --> 41:28.987
I want you to know...

41:29.020 --> 41:30.989
(sighs)

41:31.022 --> 41:32.991
...I clapped back
on those sons of bitches

41:33.024 --> 41:35.360
that put you in the hospital.

41:45.704 --> 41:48.740
Son...

41:48.774 --> 41:52.043
I want you to know I'm back now,

41:52.077 --> 41:55.881
and I need you to come back
stronger than ever.

41:58.784 --> 41:59.918
(weakly):
Pop.

42:01.419 --> 42:03.388
Son.

42:03.421 --> 42:05.390
Pop.

42:05.423 --> 42:07.693
Please don't hate me.

42:07.726 --> 42:09.861
Oh, no. I don't hate you, son.
I love you.

42:11.029 --> 42:14.199
The bomb...

42:14.232 --> 42:16.501
I-I tried to kill you.

42:16.534 --> 42:18.604
The bomb...

42:24.576 --> 42:26.477
*

42:37.656 --> 42:38.790
Lucious?

42:39.925 --> 42:41.827
Lucious?

42:46.665 --> 42:49.134
Where are you?

42:50.636 --> 42:53.238
Lucious, where are you?

43:00.946 --> 43:02.848
(grunts)

43:09.988 --> 43:12.590
Claudia?

43:12.624 --> 43:15.393
Yes, it's me.

43:15.426 --> 43:17.763
My sweet, sweet Dwight.

43:17.796 --> 43:20.932
I told you
I would never leave you.

43:20.966 --> 43:22.701
Never.

43:26.204 --> 43:27.839
Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH

44:03.474 --> 44:04.375
Yeah.

44:06.912 --> 44:08.980
Now that Empire
has you all fired up,

44:09.014 --> 44:11.516
here are a few more shows
to check out from Fox.

44:12.718 --> 44:14.052
* Uh *

44:14.085 --> 44:15.620
I guess I used to
be a scary person.

44:15.653 --> 44:17.522
* Whoo *

44:17.555 --> 44:20.491
You hurry up and fix my man,
or we gonna have a problem.

44:20.525 --> 44:24.329
They're gonna turn me
into a monster.

44:24.362 --> 44:27.665
You and me,
Cookie and Lucious forever.

44:27.699 --> 44:32.170
He doesn't even know his name.
He treats his nurse like family
and his family like strangers.

44:32.203 --> 44:33.905
We get knocked down,
we get back up.

44:35.606 --> 44:37.008
Let the games begin.

44:37.042 --> 44:40.011
ANNOUNCER:
Empire. Wednesdays on Fox.

44:40.045 --> 44:42.580
* Say it like
You really mean it *
